				<td colspan="2"><span>Stalking probes are my bread and butter when dealing with those types of rooms in high risk. Nothing beats an instant casting eye of zomm. Single target invis, cloudy potions or tiny cloak can be useful in non-undead dungeons(watch for traps!).
<br />

